016package org.talend.sdk.component.api.configuration.dependency;
017
018import java.io.Serializable;
019
020import org.talend.sdk.component.api.configuration.Option;
021import org.talend.sdk.component.api.configuration.dependency.ConnectorRef.ConnectorRefValue;
022
023import lombok.Data;
024
025/**
026 * @deprecated since 1.58.0, use {@link ConnectorRef} instead
027 */
028@Deprecated
029@Data
030public class ConnectorReference implements Serializable {
031
032    /**
033     * Family of referenced connector.
034     */
035    @Option
036    @ConnectorRef(ConnectorRefValue.FAMILY)
037    private String family;
038
039    /**
040     * Name of referenced connector.
041     */
042    @Option
043    @ConnectorRef(ConnectorRefValue.NAME)
044    private String name;
045
046    /**
047     * maven reference of referenced connector (as gav).
048     * example : org.talend.components:rest:1.29.0
049     */
050    @Option
051    @ConnectorRef(ConnectorRefValue.MAVEN_REFERENCE)
052    private String mavenReferences;
053}
